co60.mac simulates a 60Co source placed at the target position
of CeBrA. The demonstrator configuration from 2024-2025 is placed
using a geometry file: demonstrator.geo. Lead shielding bricks are
placed with bricks.geo.

The sorting code co60_sim_sort.py sorts singles spectra, with and
without energy resolution folded in, a gamma-gamma coincidence
matrix, and spectra of gamma rays collected in coincidence with
the 1332 keV transition.
